<h4>Evercam Play - IP Camera Viewer</h4>
<h5>1.2.2 Alpha 06/11</h5> 
<ul>
	<li>- Added warning dialog before leaving scanning screen<br/></li>
	<li>- Some UI changes<br/></li>
</ul>
<br/>
<b>Version 1.2.1</b>
<ul>
	<li><br/>- Fixed screen rotate issue when scanning for cameras<br/></li>
	<li>- Added no thumbnail image in scanning result<br/></li>
</ul>
<br/>
<b>Version 1.2.0</b>
<ul>
	<li><br/>- Improved scanning for cameras, it's now faster<br/></li>
	<li>- Fixed bug with Hikvision local storage<br/></li>
</ul>
<br/>
<b>Version 1.1.8 & 1.1.9</b>
<ul>
	<li><br/>- Camera list loading is faster now<br/></li>
</ul>
<br/>
<b>Version 1.1.7</b>
<ul>
	<li><br/>- First version of Hikvision local storage, you can view previously recorded footage within the app<br/></li>
</ul>
<br/>
<b>Version 1.1.6</b>
<ul>
	<li><br/>- Now you can remove cameras that are shared with you from your account<br/></li>
	<li>- Small bug fixes<br/></li>
</ul>
<br/>
<b>Version 1.1.5</b>
<ul>
	<li><br/>- Now we support more camera vendors & models<br/></li>
</ul>
<br/>
<b>Version 1.1.4</b>
<ul>
	<li><br/>- When you add a camera, we now check whether we can connect to the camera before adding it<br/></li>
	<li>- Bug fixes related to edit and remove camera.<br/></li>
</ul>
<br/>
<b>Version 1.1.3</b>
<ul>
	<li><br/>- The camera list now loads faster<br /></li>
	<li>- You can now see the details of cameras shared with you<br/></li>
	<li>- When adding cameras, you can now test local & external snapshots<br/></li>
	<li>- We've added a setting for screen sleep time<br/></li>
	<li>- Many small bug fixes<br/></li>
</ul>
<br/>
<b>Version 1.1.2</b>
<ul>
	<li><br/>- Add your IP camera<br /></li>
	<li>- Vendor/model details are now pre-populated when adding a camera<br/></li>
	<li>- Update or remove your connected IP cameras<br/></li>
	<li>- Scan your local network for IP cameras<br/></li>
	<li>- Supports digest authentication<br/></li>
	<li>- Sign in with either your email or Evercam username<br/></li>
	<li>- Now using thumbnails for scanned cameras<br/></li>
</ul>
<br />
<b>Version 1.1.1</b>
<br/>
<ul>
	<li>- You can now view multiple Evercam accounts<br/></li>
	<li>- Added ability to choose number of cameras per row</li>
	<li>- Fixed some small bugs</li>
</ul>

